Resource Profile: Visual Acuity (VA) V3 ( Experimental )

Official URL: https://larfuma.github.io/fhir-eyecare-ig/StructureDefinition-observation-visual-acuity-version-three Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2024-12-31 Computable Name: ObservationVisualAcuity_version_three
